text: Ansar al-Tawhid (Supporters of Monotheism) are a militant group in the Syrian civil war. The group is mostly made up of former Jund al-Aqsa members and the group was allied with Al-Qaeda until May 2020. The group shows sympathy to HTS and Daesh with some of their members being former members of Daesh. ==References== Category:Islamism Category:Jihadism Category:Militant groups Category:Islamist militant groups
title: Ansar al-Tawhid (Syria)
